  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<p>Ingham's self-guided tours are a fantastic way to ensure you’re making the most out of your holiday. Each of the below itineraries has been carefully put together to include the highlights of each region and take away the hassle of having to plan things for yourself.</p>
<p>With included excursions like exploring the magical city of Venice, trips on the iconic Rocky Mountaineer in Canada or Glacier Express Train in Switzerland, cruising past the Norwegian Fjords or cycling through winding forests in Chamonix, these tours promise to leave you with some incredible holiday memories. You can even spend seven days trekking through one of Italy’s most spectacular UNESCO World Heritage Sites – the Cinque Terre! With all the details taken care of including flights, accommodation and transfers, all you need to do is just have a great holiday.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Have a look at our range of Self-Guided Tours below</strong></h2>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><a name="backtotop"></a>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/8248c713ce064201b3ef305fc1a9ba75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8248c713ce064201b3ef305fc1a9ba75}" title="Cinque Terre - Self-Guided Tour">Cinque Terre<br />Italy</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/monterosso-cinque-terre/cinque-terre-self-guided-tour" title="Cinque Terre"><img src="/media/13073693/cinque-terre-2922447.jpg" alt="Cinque Terre Self Guided Tour" /></a><br />The breath-taking UNESCO site of Cinque Terre is not one to be missed. Across 3 days you can explore the region by foot, train and boat, taking in the elegance of <a data-udi="umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2}" title="Portofino">Portofino</a> and the rugged terrain of <a data-udi="umb://document/bb0a10ac87064cbb81431cb115cd10f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb0a10ac87064cbb81431cb115cd10f9}" title="Monterosso, Cinque Terre">Monterosso</a> where you’ll be based.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/8248c713ce064201b3ef305fc1a9ba75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8248c713ce064201b3ef305fc1a9ba75}" title="Cinque Terre - Self-Guided Tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/8fe668c9ecc443288d535ff4471acc74" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fe668c9ecc443288d535ff4471acc74}" title="Trekking the Cinque Terre - Self-Guided Tour">Trekking the Cinque Terre<br />Italy</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/monterosso-cinque-terre/trekking-the-cinque-terre-self-guided-tour" title="Trekking the Cinque Terre"><img src="/media/13072566/adobestock_128436397.jpeg" alt="Trekking the Cinque Terre" /></a><br />Home to some of the most picturesque walks in Italy, UNESCO site Cinque Terre is yours to explore on this week long self-guided tour. Visit the uninhabited islands, ancient monasteries and wild beaches.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/8fe668c9ecc443288d535ff4471acc74" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fe668c9ecc443288d535ff4471acc74}" title="Trekking the Cinque Terre - Self-Guided Tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9490458e18d347b69a2ef5b26124abe8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9490458e18d347b69a2ef5b26124abe8}" title="Cinque Terre and Portofino Self-Guided Tour from Sestri Levante">Cinque Terre &amp; Portofino<br />Italy</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a title="Cinque Terre &amp; Portofino"><img src="/media/13073317/portofino.jpg" alt="Cinque Terre and Portino Self-Guided Tour from Rapallo" /></a><br />From the stunning and colourful town of <a data-udi="umb://document/0fdd5a3c25b0436daa3b37ce64ccf00b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fdd5a3c25b0436daa3b37ce64ccf00b}" title="Rapallo">Rapallo</a>, spend 4 days exploring the five picturesque villages of the Cinque Terre via the funicular. You'll also take an included boat trip to the affluent Portofino where you’ll enjoy a wine tasting experience.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7f8150e04208460ca064b0634c637c75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f8150e04208460ca064b0634c637c75}" title="Cinque Terre and Portino Self-Guided Tour from Rapallo"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}" title="Lake Garda Highlights">Lake Garda Highlights<br />Italy</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/lake-garda-highlights" title="Lake Garda Highlights"><img src="/media/13074706/dsc_2417.jpg" alt="Lake Garda Highlights" /></a><br />Delve into the diversity of <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> from the bases of <a data-udi="umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b}" title="Desenzano">Desenzano</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a> on this self-guided tour. Enjoy a gondola ride on a day trip to Venice and traverse the epic Dolomites with our included excursions.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}" title="Lake Garda Highlights"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/feb62f51584048d1a8a28cca9803c563" href="/{localLink:umb://document/feb62f51584048d1a8a28cca9803c563}" title="Maggiore and Como Medley">Maggiore &amp; Como Medley<br />Italy</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-como/cadenabbia/maggiore-and-como-medley" title="Maggiore and Como Medley"><img src="/media/13074726/cadenabbia.jpg" alt="Maggiore and Como Medley" /></a><br />From the bustling town of <a data-udi="umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b}" title="Stresa">Stresa</a> to the quaint <a data-udi="umb://document/8b37cb2bfc354628b321751c199d4032" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b37cb2bfc354628b321751c199d4032}" title="Cadenabbia">Cadenabbia</a>, this is a fantastic chance to explore two of Italy’s most famous lakes and enjoy a trip on the glamorous Bernina Express.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/feb62f51584048d1a8a28cca9803c563" href="/{localLink:umb://document/feb62f51584048d1a8a28cca9803c563}" title="Maggiore and Como Medley">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line">GoldenPass Line<br />Switzerland</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/montreux/goldenpass-line" title="GoldenPass Line"><img src="/media/13074734/day-5-constance2.jpg" alt="GoldenPass Line" /></a><br />Beginning in Lake Geneva Switzerland via Interlaken all the way to Lake Lucerne. December 2022 will be an important date in the history of this line, with the launch of the GoldenPass Express. This train will connect the two tourist regions of Interlaken and Montreux without changing composition.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Glorious Glacier Express<br />Switzerland</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/interlaken/glacier-express" title="Glorious Glacier Express"><img src="/media/13074733/zermatt.jpg" alt="Glorious Glacier Express" /></a><br />Enjoy a journey on this world-famous train line and expect everything from icy glaciers, snow-dusted peaks, rushing rivers and rural hamlets.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203}" title="Iconic Mountains Tour">Iconic Mountains<br />France and Switzerland</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/chamonix/iconic-mountains-tour" title="Iconic Mountains"><img src="/media/13074735/otchamonix_gilleslansard.jpg" alt="Iconic Mountains Tour" /></a><br />Explore classy Swiss and French resorts in an awe-inspiring setting. This spectacular rail journey across the Alps takes you through the immaculate towns of <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Charmonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203}" title="Iconic Mountains Tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553}" title="Discover the Julian Alps">Discover the Julian Alps<br />Slovenia</a></h3>
<br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora/discover-the-julian-alps" title="Discover the Julian Alps"><img src="/media/13074737/photoingsibls1520jun15.jpg" alt="Discover the Julian Alps" /></a><br />You will have the opportunity to visit the fairytale destinations of <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc8e45320754ead8a9f026b9de3f1ad" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc8e45320754ead8a9f026b9de3f1ad}" title="Bovec">Bovec</a> on this self-guided holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553}" title="Discover the Julian Alps"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
